oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: King home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Exterior view of the home of Mr. and Mrs. W. R. King, grandparents of Ruth Chiles Berndt. Three men, two women and one boy with a dog are posed outside the home. One of the men is on a bicycle.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Houses; Families; Dogs; Bicycles & tricycles
